sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as KServe Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Auth as Auth Middleware<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    participant API as OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as AsyncLLM Engine (V1)
    participant Kernels as CPU Kernels<br/>C/C++ Extensions
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>PVC / S3
    participant gClient as gRPC Client
    participant gRPC as gRPC Server<br/>50051/TCP

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Loading (startup)
        Engine->>HF: GET model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HF-->>Engine: Model artifacts
        Engine->>Storage: Write to local filesystem / PVC
        Storage-->>Engine: Model loaded
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over Client,Kernels: Flow 2: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        Ingress->>Auth: Forward (TLS terminated)<br/>HTTP/8000
        Auth->>API: Validated request
        API->>Engine: Inference request<br/>(Python async, in-process)
        Engine->>Kernels: Compute attention/activation<br/>(C FFI, in-process)
        Kernels-->>Engine: Computed tensors
        Engine-->>API: Generated tokens (streaming)
        API-->>Ingress: HTTP SSE stream<br/>HTTP/8000
        Ingress-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over gClient,Kernels: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request
        gClient->>gRPC: Inference RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 50051/TCP<br/>plaintext, no auth
        gRPC->>Engine: Inference request<br/>(Python async, in-process)
        Engine->>Kernels: Compute attention/activation<br/>(C FFI, in-process)
        Kernels-->>Engine: Computed tensors
        Engine-->>gRPC: Generated tokens (streaming)
        gRPC-->>gClient: Streamed response<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 50051/TCP
    end
